txt.en: A group of mischevious young hobbits organizes a yearly secret raid of Farmer Maggot's fields, seeking to snatch wild mushrooms that grow among the grain -- and each year Farmer Maggot sets his dogs loose in the field to chase them off -- can you prove your worth as a mushroom-hunter?

Maggot's mushrooms, some of the finest mushrooms in the Shire, grow in his fields among the other crops, and young hobbits throughout the land gather to challenge each other to acts of daring and bravery whilst avoiding the nip of Farmer Maggot's dogs, Grip, Fang, and Wolf.
